/*
:name: temporal_past
:type: compile
*/
// TBD feature: temporal `past[n]` (docs/pyrope/09-verification.md, 15-tbd.md).
// past[2](a) should insert two flops so `out` is `a` delayed by 2 cycles.
// Today LiveHD cannot lower it (pass.lnastfmt: "ref text 'past[2]' is not a
// valid identifier"; bare past(a) gives upass.tolg "no hardware lowering yet").
// Tagged `fixme`: fails by design until the temporal library is implemented.
mod temporal_past(a:u8) -> (out:u8@[2]) {
  out = past[2](a)
}
